{"tid":2291474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DQ左飯民, 港共下一波會委任大量香港專業人士做傀儡治港","createTime":"2020-11-18T21:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T00:28:53.000Z","uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88c2f406e652799c467939f7137d76554f5ac319","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T21:47:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2252921/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2252921/page/1</a><br />\n我已經踢爆港台女主持林緻茵(香港願景計劃核心人物),香港願景召集人就係黨棍曾鈺成,<br />\n係節目<em>把警暴SPIN成香港示威者不滿政府下的惡意抹黑</em><br />\n<br />\n而香港願景身後就係葉國華(香港政策研究所)<br />\n-----------------------<br />\nYOUTUBER趙博都話有中間人招手,只係自己無答應到<br />\n<span class=\"red\">唔單純招安大學的人, 可以係各專業界別/ 知名YOUTUBER</span><br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">最近都見到DAB班影帝做SHOW扮屌港共,當然係西環叫班人扮, 但班人一早臭左呃唔到人<br />\n新血已經準備好埋位</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">係未來半年,香港願景等中共陰囊會玩無限銀彈係YOUTUBE出廣告,唔信大家留意下</span>"},{"pid":"bb1db3855d22b31160fcd773bd4956adb16dd443","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T21:50:53.000Z","msg":"已經有MON POST狗做野"},{"pid":"6f2b9e76c96c8045d34c0e0cd05ac043e95c3d08","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5KgUvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5KgUvh.png&h=8df44608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2sdNgJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2sdNgJD.jpg&h=62021b92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"611338c8809141c76591ac592857af758a89d680","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:20:40.000Z","msg":"<del><a href=\"http://www.hkpri.org.hk/research/detail/20201113-CSSDaOTR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkpri.org.hk%2Fresearch%2Fdetail%2F20201113-CSSDaOTR&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5lEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=bab62564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkpri.org.hk/research/detail/20201113-CSSDaOTR</a></del><br />\n要睇用VPN開<br />\n香港願景現在大JOB係老屈公務員宣誓做黨員<br />\n------------<br />\n同埋香港願景上線香港政策研究所攪左「全民國家安全教育日二零二零徵文比賽」<br />\n超過300個後生報名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RY0Tck4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRY0Tck4.jpg&h=24ebe35e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSam Chan<br />\n我 衰左。。下年再努力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100017348431695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D100017348431695&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5lEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=240ecba8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100017348431695</a><br />\n--------------"},{"pid":"69f5a0a177a9771c49e0ed3d07bda13085723c1d","tid":2291474,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:24:55.000Z","msg":"sam chan<br />\n一睇就知係自戀自大自我中心再加智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dd84b6695fc594feb7e61f89c070bc95b0e201","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:31:23.000Z","msg":"會員熊貓都係貓 #94184支持特赦黑警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2291480/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2291480/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警魔係握公權力下強姦,殺人<br />\n係反人類暴行<br />\n<br />\n而示威者至今未有造成人命傷亡<br />\n係有大量假ACC故意混淆<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n去到特赦示威者就係香港人上風<br />\n<br />\n當日香港警魔輪姦婦女仲搵黨委法官出搜查令迫害受害人<br />\n故意唔告恐怖份子鄭國泉<br />\n<br />\n姐係身為受害人掌權後追究就叫無法治?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046683/page/7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046683/page/7</a><br />\n#150<br />\n熊貓都係貓<br />\n&bull;<br />\n5 個月前<br />\n嚟緊嗰節輪到楊岳橋難拆<br />\n特赦就咁聽落係違反佢自己所講嘅法律面前人人平等<br />\n其實講真，你話要特赦全部示威者，然後只告藍絲，黑警，呢樣真係好難去話唔破壞法治，甚至實行上都好困難。<br />\n解決方法唯有係獨立調查委員會照做報告都照出，睇下邊啲黑警真係要負責，但又唔提告，示威者都特赦，即係兩邊都特赦，但警隊都要重組去改善避免下次再有。一係就兩邊照告，但唔涉及暴力既特</del>"},{"pid":"ee52373f7df3e681fd245331641f5eec60ed2e0a","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:46:20.000Z","msg":"我曾經研究過大量提倡兩邊特赦的垃圾會員的帳號<br />\n絕大部分係空白帳戶<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>偶有發言者都從不譴責警暴</strong><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ac1804bf02cd2e44bb9610b136706f87b422afa1","tid":2291474,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14102e731c6b994e9ab27801ab7b463f5e06c923","tid":2291474,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"94dd84b6695fc594feb7e61f89c070bc95b0e201","tid":2291474,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:31:23.000Z","msg":"會員熊貓都係貓 #94184支持特赦黑警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2291480/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2291480/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警魔係握公權力下強姦,殺人<br />\n係反人類暴行<br />\n<br />\n而示威者至今未有造成人命傷亡<br />\n係有大量假ACC故意混淆<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n去到特赦示威者就係香港人上風<br />\n<br />\n當日香港警魔輪姦婦女仲搵黨委法官出搜查令迫害受害人<br />\n故意唔告恐怖份子鄭國泉<br />\n<br />\n姐係身為受害人掌權後追究就叫無法治?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046683/page/7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046683/page/7</a><br />\n#150<br />\n熊貓都係貓<br